<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Trainer's Cheat Sheet</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="cheatsheet.css">
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>Trainer's Cheat Sheet</h1>
    <p>Quick reference for essential gym details</p>
  </header>
  <main>
    <section class="category">
      <h2>Gym Equipment</h2>
      <div class="card-container">
        <div class="card">
          <img src="../server/assets/treadmill.jpg" alt="Treadmill">
          <h3>Treadmill</h3>
          <p>Perfect for cardio and endurance training.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <img src="../server/assets/dumbells.jpg" alt="Dumbbells">
          <h3>Dumbbells</h3>
          <p>Versatile equipment for strength training.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <img src="../server/assets/benchpress.jpg" alt="Bench Press">
          <h3>Bench Press</h3>
          <p>Build chest and upper body strength.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <img src="../server/assets/cablemachine.jpg" alt="Cable Machine">
          <h3>Cable Machine</h3>
          <p>Great for targeted muscle isolation exercises.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <img src="../server/assets/rowingmachine.jpg" alt="Rowing Machine">
          <h3>Rowing Machine</h3>
          <p>Combines cardio and full-body strength training.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <img src="../server/assets/legpress.jpg" alt="Leg Press">
          <h3>Leg Press</h3>
          <p>Target your quadriceps, hamstrings, and calves.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <img src="../server/assets/pullupbar.jpg" alt="Pull-Up Bar">
          <h3>Pull-Up Bar</h3>
          <p>Build upper body and core strength.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <img src="../server/assets/kettlebell.jpg" alt="Kettlebells">
          <h3>Kettlebells</h3>
          <p>Improve functional strength and endurance.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="category">
      <h2>Exercises</h2>
      <div class="card-container">
        <div class="card">
          <img src="../server/assets/squats.jpg" alt="Squats">
          <h3>Squats</h3>
          <p>Build lower body strength and core stability.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <img src="../server/assets/deadlift.jpg" alt="Deadlifts">
          <h3>Deadlifts</h3>
          <p>Essential for full-body strength development.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <img src="../server/assets/plank.jpg" alt="Plank">
          <h3>Plank</h3>
          <p>Core-strengthening exercise to improve stability.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <img src="../server/assets/lunges.jpg" alt="Lunges">
          <h3>Lunges</h3>
          <p>Enhance balance and lower body strength.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <img src="../server/assets/pushups.jpg" alt="Push-Ups">
          <h3>Push-Ups</h3>
          <p>A classic exercise for upper body strength.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <img src="../server/assets/rowing.jpg" alt="Rowing">
          <h3>Rowing</h3>
          <p>Effective for back and arm muscle strength.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <img src="../server/assets/mountainclimber.jpg" alt="Mountain Climbers">
          <h3>Mountain Climbers</h3>
          <p>Boost agility and cardiovascular fitness.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <img src="../server/assets/burpees.jpg" alt="Burpees">
          <h3>Burpees</h3>
          <p>Full-body workout for endurance and strength.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="category">
      <h2>Meal Planning and Nutrition</h2>
      <div class="card-container">
        <div class="card">
          <img src="../server/assets/highproteinmeal.jpg" alt="High Protein Meal">
          <h3>High Protein Meal</h3>
          <p>Boost muscle recovery and growth with lean protein sources.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <img src="../server/assets/lowcarbmeal.jpg" alt="Low Carb Meal">
          <h3>Low Carb Meal</h3>
          <p>Supports weight management and fat loss goals.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <img src="../server/assets/preworkoutsnack.jpg" alt="Pre-Workout Snack">
          <h3>Pre-Workout Snack</h3>
          <p>Fuel workouts with a mix of carbs and protein.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <img src="../server/assets/postworkoutmeal.jpg" alt="Post-Workout Meal">
          <h3>Post-Workout Meal</h3>
          <p>Replenish energy and repair muscles after exercise.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="category">
      <h2>Safety</h2>
      <div class="card-container">
        <div class="card">
          <img src="../server/assets/firstaidkit.jpg" alt="First Aid">
          <h3>First Aid Kit</h3>
          <p>Ensure a well-stocked first aid kit is always available.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <img src="../server/assets/spotterassistance.jpg" alt="Spotter Assistance">
          <h3>Spotter Assistance</h3>
          <p>Provide help during heavy lifting to prevent injuries.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <img src="../server/assets/streching.jpg" alt="Stretching">
          <h3>Stretching</h3>
          <p>Reduce injury risks with pre- and post-workout stretching.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <img src="../server/assets/stayhydrated.jpg" alt="Stay Hydrated">
          <h3>Stay Hydrated</h3>
          <p>Encourage adequate water intake during workouts.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
